description.en: The payment network which will plant unlimited trees, it's about #conservation, for the #future of everyone. Carboncoin provides seamless round-the-clock value storage and transfer services, and has been since February 2014. Based on the Bitcoin protocol, Carboncoin has eliminated mining for profit – the aspect of cryptocurrencies responsible for harming the environment, through wastage of electricity.
